#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:10
msgid "Browser Extension"
msgstr "浏览器扩展"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:11
msgid ""
"The browser extension allows you to quickly add new bookmarks without "
"leaving the page that you are on. The extension is available in the official "
"extension stores for:"
msgstr "浏览器扩展可以让你不离开当前页面就添加书签，已在官方商店上架："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:15
msgid "Firefox"
msgstr "Firefox"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:19
msgid "Chrome"
msgstr "Chrome"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:22
msgid ""
"The extension is <a href=\"https://github.com/sissbruecker/linkding-"
"extension\" target=\"_blank\">open source</a> as well, which enables you to "
"build and manually load it into any browser that supports Chrome extensions."
msgstr "该扩展也是<a href=\"https://github.com/sissbruecker/linkding-extension\" target=\"_blank\">开源</a>的，可自行构建并在支持 Chrome 扩展的浏览器中手动加载。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:23
msgid "Bookmarklet"
msgstr "书签小工具"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:24
msgid ""
"The bookmarklet is an alternative, cross-browser way to quickly add new "
"bookmarks without opening the linkding application first. Here's how it "
"works:"
msgstr "Bookmarklet 是一种跨浏览器的快捷添加方式，无需先打开 linkding 应用，使用步骤："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:27
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred method for detecting website titles and descriptions "
"below"
msgstr "选择用于获取网页标题与描述的方式："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:29
msgid "Help"
msgstr "帮助"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:31
msgid "Drag the bookmarklet below into your browser's bookmark bar / toolbar"
msgstr "把下面的 bookmarklet 拖到浏览器书签栏/工具栏"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:32
msgid "Open the website that you want to bookmark"
msgstr "打开想要收藏的网页"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:33
msgid "Click the bookmarklet in your browser's toolbar"
msgstr "点击工具栏中的 bookmarklet"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:34
msgid ""
"linkding opens in a new window or tab and allows you to add a bookmark for "
"the site"
msgstr "linkding 会在新窗口/标签打开，让你为该站点添加书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:35
msgid ""
"After saving the bookmark, the linkding window closes, and you are back on "
"your website"
msgstr "保存后 linkding 窗口会关闭，你将回到原网站"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:40
msgid "Choose your preferred bookmarklet:"
msgstr "选择偏好的 bookmarklet："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:48
msgid "Detect title and description on the server"
msgstr "在服务器端提取标题和描述"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:56
msgid "Detect title and description in the browser"
msgstr "在浏览器端提取标题和描述"

