msgid "REST API"
msgstr "REST API"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:102
msgid "Copy this token now, it will only be shown once:"
msgstr "请立即复制此令牌，只会显示一次："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:104
msgid "New token key"
msgstr "新令牌值"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:110
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "复制"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:114
msgid ""
"API tokens can be used to authenticate 3rd-party applications against the "
"REST API. <strong>Please treat tokens as you would any other credential.</"
"strong> Any party with access to a token can access and manage all your "
"bookmarks."
msgstr "API 令牌用于第三方应用访问 REST API。<strong>请像对待其他凭证一样保护令牌。</strong>任何获得令牌的人都可访问并管理你的全部书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:122
msgid "Name"
msgstr "名称"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:123
msgid "Created"
msgstr "创建时间"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:125
#| msgid "Active"
msgid "Actions"
msgstr "当前收藏"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:150
msgid "Create API token"
msgstr "创建 API 令牌"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:175
msgid "RSS Feeds"
msgstr "RSS 订阅"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:176
msgid "The following URLs provide RSS feeds for your bookmarks:"
msgstr "以下链接提供你的书签 RSS 订阅："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:179
#| msgid "Add bookmark"
msgid "All bookmarks"
msgstr "添加收藏"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:182
#| msgid "Shared bookmarks"
msgid "Unread bookmarks"
msgstr "共享书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:185
#: bookmarks/templates/shared/nav_menu.html:94 bookmarks/views/contexts.py:334
msgid "Shared bookmarks"
msgstr "共享书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:188
msgid "Public shared bookmarks"
msgstr "公开共享书签"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:190
msgid ""
"The public shared feed does not contain an authentication token and can be "
"shared with other people. Only shows shared bookmarks from users who have "
"explicitly enabled public sharing."
msgstr "公开共享订阅不含鉴权令牌，可与他人分享；仅包含明确开启公开分享的用户书签。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:193
msgid "All URLs support the following URL parameters:"
msgstr "所有订阅链接支持以下参数："

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:196
msgid ""
"A <code>limit</code> parameter for specifying the maximum number of "
"bookmarks to include in the feed. By default, only the latest 100 matching "
"bookmarks are included."
msgstr "<code>limit</code>：最多包含多少条书签，默认最新 100 条。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:199
msgid ""
"A <code>q</code> URL parameter for specifying a search query. You can get an "
"example by doing a search in the bookmarks view and then copying the "
"parameter from the URL."
msgstr "<code>q</code>：搜索查询参数，可在书签页搜索后从地址栏复制示例。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:202
msgid ""
"An <code>unread</code> parameter for filtering for unread or read bookmarks. "
"Use <code>yes</code> for unread bookmarks and <code>no</code> for read "
"bookmarks."
msgstr "<code>unread</code>：筛选未读/已读，使用 <code>yes</code> 表示未读，<code>no</code> 表示已读。"

#: bookmarks/templates/settings/integrations.html:205
msgid ""
"A <code>shared</code> parameter for filtering for shared or unshared "
"bookmarks. Use <code>yes</code> for shared bookmarks and <code>no</code> for "
"unshared bookmarks."
msgstr "<code>shared</code>：筛选共享/未共享，使用 <code>yes</code> 表示共享，<code>no</code> 表示未共享。"

